                            "text": ": Strom."
                        },
                        {
                            "verse": 39,
                            "chapter": 1,
                            "name": "Tatian: Fragments 1:39",
                            "text": ", iii  9  Tatian condemns and rejects not only marriage, but also meats which God has created for use."
                        },
                        {
                            "verse": 40,
                            "chapter": 1,
                            "name": "Tatian: Fragments 1:40",
                            "text": "—Hieron."
                        },
                        {
